<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title || "Home" %></title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/styles.css">
  <script src="js/script.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
<div class="body-wrapper">
  <header>
    <div class="log-login-wrapper">
      <a href="/" class="logo">CSE Motors</a>
      <div class="login-wrapper">
        <a href="#">My Account</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <nav>
      <ul>
        <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Custom</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Sedan</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">SUV</a></li>
        <li><a href="#">Truck</a></li>
      </ul>
    </nav>
  </header>
  <main>
    <section class="card">
      <h2>Welcome to CSE Motors!</h2>
      <div class="ad-card">
        <h3>DMC Delorian</h3>
        <p>3 Cup holders</p>
        <p>Superman doors</p>
        <p>Fuzzy dice!</p>
        <button class="ad-btn">Own Today</button>
      </div>
      <img src="/images/vehicles/delorean.jpg" alt="">
    </section>

    <div class="content">
      <section>
        <h2>DMC Delorian Reviews</h2>
        <ul class="bullet-points">
          <li>"So fast it's almost like travveling in time." (4/5)</li>
          <li>"Coolest ride on the road." (4/5)</li>
          <li>"I'm feeling McFly!" (5/5)</li>
          <li>"The most futuristic ride of our day." (4.5/5)</li>
          <li>"80's living and I love it!" (5/5)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>
  
      <section>
        <h2>Delorian Upgrades</h2>
        <div class="grid">
          <div class="grid-item">
            <div class="grid-item-img">
              <img src="/images/upgrades/flux-cap.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <a href="#">Flux Capacitor</a>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-item">
            <div class="grid-item-img">
              <img src="/images/upgrades/flame.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <a href="#">Flame Decals</a>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-item">
            <div class="grid-item-img">
              <img src="/images/upgrades/bumper_sticker.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <a href="#">Bumper Stickers</a>
          </div>
          <div class="grid-item">
            <div class="grid-item-img">
              <img src="/images/upgrades/hub-cap.jpg" alt="">
            </div>
            <a href="#">Hub Caps</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </main>
  <footer>
    <p>Â© 2025, CSE 340 App</p>
  </footer>
</div>
</body>
</html>
